            B:"格式（JSON、XML、markdown 結構符號會額外消耗 tokens）", B_en:"Format (JSON, XML, markdown syntax adds tokens)",
            C:"whitespace（多餘換行、縮排會被計入）", C_en:"Whitespace (extra newlines, indentation count)",
            D:"程式碼語法（特殊符號、reserved keywords 對 BPE/SentencePiece 切分不同）", D_en:"Code syntax (special chars, keywords tokenize differently in BPE/SentencePiece)",
