            stem_en:"[Advanced] Which best describes the difference and priority between system prompt and user prompt?",
            A:"system prompt 設定角色、行為準則與恆定限制，優先級高於 user prompt；廠商通常透過 RLHF 訓練模型優先遵循 system 指令以對抗 prompt injection", A_en:"System prompt sets role, behavior, and constant constraints — it has higher priority than user prompt; RLHF training makes models prefer system instructions to resist prompt injection",
